riodically for any changes. You are bound by any changes to the privacy policy when you use Our Application, Product or Service after such changes have been first posted.</p><p>11. How do we Contact You</p><p>E-mail and other communications:</p><p> &nbsp;</p><p> We may contact you, by email or other means; for example, we, or persons we share your Personal Information with may send you promotional offers on behalf of other businesses, or communicate with you about your use of the Application or the Product. Also, we may receive confirmation when you open an email from us. This confirmation helps us make emails more interesting and improve our service. If you do not want to receive email or other mail from us, please indicate your preference by emailing us at contact@askpinkypromise.com.</p><p> &nbsp;</p><p>12. Contact Us</p><p>If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@askpinkypromise.com">contact@askpinkypromise.com</a>.</p><p>Our Products are manufactured by Elegant Global Cosmetics, having address at – Shri Arihant Complex, Gala No. 10 and 11, Building No. C-14, Kalher, Bhiwandi, 428 302; and are only marketed by Us, therefore, cases of any Product related issue or emergency shall be addressed to them.</p>
